After the selections described in Sect. 6.1.1 are applied to the data, the three samples still contain background originating from hadrons misidentified as electrons as well as from true electrons from photon conversions and non-isolated electrons originating from heavy-flavour decays. For each sample and in each (ET,η)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
